Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.02,0:00:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.04,0:00:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 是法式吐司的说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.69,0:00:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好红
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.14,0:00:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然不用做午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.66,0:00:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把工夫都下在早饭上了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.22,0:00:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你下的不是工夫…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是披萨酱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开吃喽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂糖吐司本来就甜 披萨酱让它甜上加甜！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.86,0:00:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？味道很怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.65,0:00:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…不 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.78,0:00:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体有点不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.46,0:00:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了吗？是不是该请个病假呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你操心了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不要紧吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.22,0:00:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.18,0:01:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.59,0:01:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸色好差 在家歇着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.62,0:01:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用不用 身体好得很
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.12,0:01:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,披萨酱…看我怎么封印你
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------OPCN----------------------------
