Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.21,0:01:35.59,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}无情地发出宣告
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:48.45,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}你用双耳 独自聆听着什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:02:01.30,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我的眼睛 映照出久远的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:04.65,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}选择什么 放弃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.67,0:02:07.86,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我如何能 自行定夺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.88,0:02:11.07,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}选取之物 早已在心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.09,0:02:14.00,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}向神问询 是否有误
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:17.12,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}其实不曾孤独过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.29,0:02:19.67,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}其实一直在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:26.74,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}现在 伸出手去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:29.98,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}已经无所畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:33.49,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}哪怕化身怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.53,0:02:41.57,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我一定 会做到
