Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着听着 有个大新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西森柚咲要转过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？柚咲琳吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 这又不是艺校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 如果是真的就太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:02:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是柚咲琳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.64,0:02:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,群情激动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等她来了 得闹成什么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想都烦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个 回座位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.98,0:03:08.38,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 该不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:11.38,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊 哇噻…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.49,0:03:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.94,0:03:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今天有位新同学转到了我们班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是柚咲琳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑羽柚咲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静 安静！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 快坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你 别跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里也自称「柚咲琳」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真名叫黑羽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 居然连这都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然 我有时会因为工作不能来上学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 还是很期待和各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共度愉快的高中生活哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲琳 柚咲琳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲琳 柚咲琳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲琳 柚咲琳…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.47,0:03:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我安静点！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑羽的座位在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会有许多不周到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她算个球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么转过来？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我预订了你的新单曲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也订了 那首歌真好听
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「早气」 我一直在看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交个朋友吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请和我交换邮件地址…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 突然说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.61,0:04:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想浑水摸鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位同学 要友好相处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？难道要使「那个」了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.47,0:04:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？使什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和好如初
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和好如初
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和好如初的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲琳的小魔法之13
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和好如初的魔法！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:04:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位和好如初喽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也有错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞啥啊 什么小魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲同学曾作为固定班底
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参演早间新闻节目「早间气氛」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在「早气」里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她会对着占卜环节里显示有霉运的观众
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用一系列小魔法！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是13 总共有几个啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,64个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这里面有重复
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实质上只有63…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 协助者又要来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…你干嘛啊 学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑羽同学 请马上和我去学生会室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会长大人 你也太不上路子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲同学 刚才的小魔法之13
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和好如初的魔法 真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:05:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道得真清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲同学参演时 我每期必看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 谢谢你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么追星 高城你好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在这里做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协助者就快来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.66,0:06:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请注意 不要被他那异常的外表吓到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好心理准备…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放心 他也是伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会害人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力是 念动力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…到底发生了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他告诉我们 有特殊能力者在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力是念动力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像这样 你也是由他找出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲琳也要加油喽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是没这意识而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.71,0:07:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你既能通灵又能生火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个更厉害的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标在学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.11,0:07:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关内学园
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 中了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？中了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.89,0:07:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喏 上周的体育报
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.37,0:07:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连续3场完全比赛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.37,0:07:32.67,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,550)\an8\fs56\fscx92\fsp0}完全比赛：一局中不让对方任何球员到达一垒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶球威力惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必将进军职业联赛的超高中级投手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第二天就去看他训练了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位也来看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.82,0:07:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播放
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害的变化球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大联盟级别的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而事情不简单
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:08:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来看看投手的手部特写
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.74,0:08:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是直球的握法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从头到尾都是这握法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶球的重点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在于减少球的旋转 让球路无法预测
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本都是用食指和中指抵在球上再扔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用直球握法投球 会让球旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会出现刚才那种不稳定的球路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的真多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 他投球后在用念动力控球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 你也很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的听懂了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须在甲子园预选赛开始前控制住他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们马上出发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？课呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我们隶属学生会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管干什么都不会影响成绩和档案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是星海学园学生会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在训练呢 什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西森柚咲？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管她 先听我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开门见山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的蝴蝶球是用念动力搞出来的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念动力？你是说超能力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能有超能力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是学生会 你们其实是灵异研究会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你给我听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的能力 只不过是青春期里的一种「病」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你想当职业选手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了那时也没能力可用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 如果有人注意到了你的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就会被抓起来 变得再也无法打棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 今后请不要再使用特殊能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓起来？被谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一群科学家 专门研究你这种能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.91,0:09:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我信你的蠢话？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:09:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子真不识相
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤熟得了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.28,0:10:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…呃 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在这种地方秀能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 呸！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 柚咲琳的唾液！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 应该算美砂的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何去何从啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:28.21,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这…从本质上来看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:32.02,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是柚咲琳的唾液
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:36.94,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 或许我该忘了这唾液…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续说正事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 到底该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就比棒球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两边学校的棒球部之间 来场比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们赢了 就听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们赢了 就别再管我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你又当不了职业球手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么拼？令人费解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:10:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了去甲子园
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就周日下午三点 在我校操场比好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有史 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们学校的棒球部里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人能扔那种蝴蝶球？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以用能力 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗬 都会使些什么能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.36,0:11:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本校棒球部的球员都只有可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不会使用能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么打？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也要打？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在我们的操场上打 不会出乱子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很合适
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 难得能让我燃一把
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.69,0:11:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许燃一根毛！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------TXTB----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.71,0:12:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:06.97,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.57,0:12:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对面还有女生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们肯定打不回你的球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种比赛有意义吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是为了将来 隆人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你这么说 那就上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果输了 球棒揍屁股是逃不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神 噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球棒揍屁股…好古老的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我们投手扔的球都打不回
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对面的击球手好烂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仓促出战 我们还这么认真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能说这种话！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 小心我罢赛！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就糟了 请继续投球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:12:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你说话前动动脑子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑羽同学 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变魔法 变魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静头脑的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲琳小魔法之9！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静头脑的魔法！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 你冷静下来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球 击球手出局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是正牌蝴蝶球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不可能打得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想揍屁股就揍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 居然能把那种球全都接住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕手也是超高中级的么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无胜算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿一分就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.09,0:13:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要由我们俩拿一分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再由我们俩守住分差
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就赢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然盯上柚咲了么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 美砂很有运动细胞的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 柚咲的肩膀使不上劲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 能判断却没力气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球 击球手出局
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出局
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太凶险了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也用能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具体怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你入侵对面的击球手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩两名击球手 懒洋洋地挥棒就行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你扔坏球就行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意别暴投
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.09,0:15:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.46,0:15:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要用能力来干这种事么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两好球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一下就两人出局了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有史 既然你如此坚决地求胜…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.91,0:16:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦！干得好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隆人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么安全？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到这一招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盗本垒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 该死该死！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下赢不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球 击球手出局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想办法打出触击球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再使用能力 跑过一垒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们看得到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会用超高速摄像录下证据
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两好球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再失败就出局了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩一个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 他碰到一垒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喏喏 安全吧？安全吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到…到底怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 你的牺牲不会白费
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.69,0:17:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人 换上！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲没有力气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我会打出我的味道！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.02,0:17:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害 像一朗一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:37.21,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,450)\an8\fs58\fscx92\fsp1}铃木一朗：传奇球手，安打制造机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮到你击球了 怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的触击牺牲打成功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再来个安打就能逆转胜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的能力可打不到那种球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔动动真格如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.24,0:17:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作弊狂魔乙坂有宇同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我中！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 竟然让这种人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:11.52,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一垒！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种局面动真格…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.46,0:18:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利利利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.46,0:18:24.32,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,450)\an8\fs58\fscx92\fsp0}利利利：即「局势对我们有利」，给敌投手施压
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两好球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.67,0:18:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于打到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.21,0:18:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机越抓越准
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一球要变得更多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没结束 快跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死三振！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行！跑出我的味道！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隆人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛结束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是！我的味道！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲琳好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我们赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.11,0:19:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 赢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 为什么要为此高兴？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的能力 今后不许再用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.24,0:20:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直是个平庸的投手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 捕手隆人和我不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他应该受人瞩目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我俩一直是搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:16.11,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:17.11,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.39,0:20:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知我们的棒球部很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他依然选择了和我搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜用上神奇的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想带他一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着他 去职业人士关注的大舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.36,0:20:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你使用能力不是出于私欲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是为了朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的比赛 我们是靠作弊赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的投球也一直是靠作弊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.94,0:20:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 总有人会注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用作弊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到上了大学 进了社会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你照样可以做他的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他打棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:21:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以自豪地说「那是我的挚友」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对可以 一定行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做个小实验吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能入侵他一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了 是个小实验
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对实验对象说这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验对象是他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.06,0:21:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.97,0:21:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 不谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞清楚什么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.99,0:21:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要观察一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 晚饭里不要有披萨酱！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.86,0:21:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:21:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙坂家秘传 加量版奶油炖西兰花的说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.28,0:21:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好红
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.99,0:22:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶油炖菜应该是白色的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.86,0:22:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呀 是乙坂家秘传的说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.62,0:22:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.49,0:22:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问我相信什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.54,0:22:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能相信我自己呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.96,0:22:14.93,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信的力量 挑战的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.68,0:22:20.26,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏季招生 火热进行中…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.92,0:22:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 柚咲琳的新广告
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.67,0:22:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是哈罗哈罗的新曲！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 柚咲琳真的转学过来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.91,0:22:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.40,0:22:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不得的说！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------EDCN----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.81,0:22:43.25,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(150,150)}如果我说 旅途的艰险等在前方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.31,0:22:49.14,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(150,150)}你一定 会如此斥责我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:55.79,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(150,150)}你会说 活着就是残酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:23:02.30,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(150,150)}你会说 谁都有切肤之痛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.68,0:23:06.97,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(150,150)}总有一天 我要向你展示
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.00,0:23:14.34,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(150,150)}展示一件 珍藏心中之物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.63,0:23:22.97,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(150,150)}独一无二的奔流 涌现后便即消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.15,0:23:29.31,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(150,150)}经历着失去的你 默默遥望云端
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.50,0:23:35.62,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(150,150)}你一定 还在坚信乐园定能到达
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.61,0:23:58.38,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(150,150)}你一定 是为藏在深处的我欢笑至今
